title: Lesson 02 - One Minute Romanian
description: In lesson 2 of One Minute Romanian you will learn a few more useful words in Romanian which you'll use every day. Remember - even a few phrases of a language can help you make friends and enjoy travel more. Find out more about One Minute Romanian at our website - http://www.oneminutelanguages.com. itunes:summary: Join Romanian teacher Roxana and presenter Mark as they teach you the basics of Romanian. In this podcast you'll be learning just enough Romanian to get by on a holiday or business trip to Romania, or just to impress Romanian speakers everywhere! Each lesson includes just over one minute of language-learning content, so there's no excuse not to learn! Remember - even a few phrases of a language can help you make friends and enjoy travel more.
